&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Dec 2012 16:49:17 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/asl/noticias/11a-oid-foi-um-sucesso</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/asl/noticias/11a-oid-foi-um-sucesso</guid></item></channel></rss>